## 2) Hero Slideshow Header
Section file: `sections/hero-slideshow-header.liquid`

### What this section is for
Sticky header + full hero slideshow with shared text and shared CTA.

### Main editable components in Shopify
- Header: `Logo`, `Menu`, `Text Color`.
- Button defaults and primary button color overrides.
- Button border and typography settings.
- Shared content for all slides:
  - `Shared Title`, `Shared Subtitle`
  - `Shared Button Text`, `Shared Button Link`
  - `Shared Title Color`, `Shared Subtitle Color`
  - `Title & Subtitle Position`
  - `Title & Subtitle Alignment` (`left/center/right/justify`)
  - Custom X/Y controls for text and button positions.
- Button sizing and shape: vertical offset, radius, width/height, glassy style.
- Slideshow behavior: `Slide Height`, autoplay enable/speed.

### Block components
Block type: `Slide`
- `Image (Desktop)`, `Image (Mobile)`.
- Per-slide text/button fields exist as fallback seeds if shared fields are empty.

### Usage notes
- Prefer shared title/subtitle/button for consistent messaging.
- Use `Shared ... Position` + alignment together for final layout.
- Use mobile image for better crop/composition on small screens.

