## 3) Hers Labs Hero
Section file: `sections/hers-labs-hero.liquid`

### What this section is for
Large branded hero with background, character image, and marquee-style sliding cards.

### Main editable components in Shopify
- Background image + desktop/mobile background heights.
- Section height desktop/mobile.
- Section padding top/bottom.
- Characters image, alt text, max width desktop/mobile.
- Sliding image speed.
- Sliding track/image size and gaps desktop/mobile.

### Block components
Block type: `Sliding Image`
- Image + alt text.

Block type: `Small Screen Controls`
- Extra scaling/size controls for very small screens:
  - character max width/scale
  - sliding scale/track height/width/height/gap

### Usage notes
- Keep at least several `Sliding Image` blocks for smooth marquee continuity.
- Use `Small Screen Controls` to tune compact laptop and narrow mobile behavior.

