## 4) Shop Color Grid
Section file: `sections/shop-color-grid.liquid`

### What this section is for
Interactive product grid with age filtering and optional quick-add popup.

### Main editable components in Shopify
- Visibility: `Hide on mobile`.
- Typography: global font and multiple weight controls.
- Heading: text and color.
- Age filter: title, button colors/radius, reset icon.
- Filter button 1/2/3 labels + ranges.
- Quick add popup: enable, title, icon size, size guide labels/image.
- Layout/colors: section background, section padding/margins.
- Heading area padding and age filter margins.
- Mobile carousel paddings.
- Grid wrapper paddings.
- Grid controls: vertical align, top offset, max width, gap, columns.
- Tile visuals: aspect ratios, mobile height fallback, tile bg, image fit, base zoom, hover zoom, radius, overlay opacity.

### Block components
Block type: `Product tile`
- Product
- Optional custom image
- Hover text color
- `Age Range(s)` mapping

### Usage notes
- Make sure filter ranges match tile `Age Range(s)` values exactly.
- Keep quick-add enabled only if variant selection UX is desired.

