## 5) Product Glass Card
Section file: `sections/product-glass-card.liquid`

### What this section is for
Feature-rich product section with gallery and glassmorphism details panel.

### Main editable components in Shopify
- Section background color/gradient, min height, container/padding.
- Middle split-word visual controls (text, size, opacity, blur, clipping, shifts).
- Gallery controls: image sizes, radius, arrows.
- Glass card controls: bg color/gradient, border radius, opacity/blur, border style, mobile blur/opacity factors.
- Typography and text sizing (title, price, minimal price).
- CTA text and button text color.
- Payment icons (COD, Whish).
- Product title behavior (`append_color_option`).
- Size guide controls (image, heading, heading style, spacing, alignment).
- Fit area label and selected size toggle.
- Accordion fallback headings and accordion typography/height.

### Block components
Block type: `Dropdown / Accordion`
- Heading
- Content source type
- Optional custom HTML content

Block type: `Payment method`
- Label
- Icon

### Usage notes
- If metafields exist for product-specific styling, they can override some section defaults.
- Keep accordion content concise for better mobile readability.

