## 6) Center Product Carousel
Section file: `sections/center-product-carousel.liquid`

### What this section is for
Centered horizontal product carousel with customizable cards and media sources.

### Main editable components in Shopify
- Heading/subheading + alignment and heading style.
- Card layout: gap, radius, width.
- Product metadata visibility: vendor and swatches toggles.
- Card content panel styling (bg/text/border/padding/margin).
- Navigation controls: arrows (style/size/colors), dots.
- Autoplay toggle and speed.
- Bottom spacing.

### Block components
Block type: `Product`
- Product
- Optional badge text
- Media source selector
- Optional custom media/GIF/video inputs
- Optional placeholder image for remote GIF flows
- Alt text
- Focal position

### Usage notes
- For best performance, avoid heavy remote GIFs on many cards simultaneously.
- Keep autoplay moderate when showing detailed product info.

