## 7) Clickable Lookbook
Section file: `sections/section-clickable-lookbook.liquid`

### What this section is for
Single hero image with clickable hotspots linking to products.

### Main editable components in Shopify
- Section background color.
- Main image dimensions and border radius.
- Hotspot color and desktop size.
- Section top/bottom padding.

### Block components
Block type: `Main Image`
- Desktop image
- Optional mobile image

Block type: `Hotspot`
- Linked product
- Desktop X/Y position
- Optional separate mobile X/Y position
- Tooltip controls: position, title/price/CTA sizes, bg/text colors

### Usage notes
- On mobile: first tap reveals tooltip, second tap navigates.
- Keep hotspots away from image edges to avoid tooltip clipping.

