## 8) Hex Prism Carousel
Section file: `sections/hex-prism-carousel.liquid`

### What this section is for
3D prism-style rotating carousel with optional age filter and quick add.

### Main editable components in Shopify
- 3D geometry: perspective/radius desktop/mobile.
- Card sizing: width/height desktop/mobile and optional aspect ratio.
- Card spacing and corner radius.
- Section title text/style and spacing.
- Side face opacity controls.
- Image max width and section background.
- Desktop visibility toggle and section paddings.
- Age filter controls (title styles, values, scale, spacing, reset icon).
- Carousel box scale and card name typography.
- Quick add + size guide controls.

### Block components
Block type: `Card`
- Name
- Ages
- Image
- Link
- Optional product for quick add
- Gradient start/end

### Usage notes
- Keep `age_filter_values` synchronized with each card `ages` value.
- Use moderate perspective/radius to avoid overlap on smaller screens.

