## 9) Footer
Section file: `sections/footer.liquid`

### What this section is for
Global footer with brand/company/policies/newsletter/social/payment/localization and visual styling.

### Main editable components in Shopify
- Color scheme and newsletter enable/heading.
- Brand/company/policies/newsletter labels and fallback links.
- Policies custom menu.
- Copyright text (supports placeholders like `[year]`, `[shop_name]`).
- Social controls (including WhatsApp link).
- Country/language selectors.
- Payment display toggle and payment paddings.
- Policy links toggle.
- Background style group:
  - glassy background
  - bg image
  - gradient toggle/css
  - bg color/text color
  - opacity/blur/border settings
- Typography group:
  - heading/body/button fonts
  - title/link/newsletter/bottom text sizes and weights
- Spacing:
  - section margin top
  - padding top/bottom

### Footer block components
- `Link list`: heading + menu + optional mobile custom menu usage.
- `Brand information`: social visibility toggle.
- `Text`: heading + rich text content.
- `Image`: image + width + alignment.
- `Payment option`: label + icon + link.
- `@app`: app embed block (if used by installed apps).

